<emphasis id="B908EA89B733966B22EECCD2FC79BDDD" box="[927,1021,1445,1469]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">ex larva</emphasis>
, Touroult leg. (
<collectionCode id="ED6DAE5EB733966B25C0CCD1FB7BBDDE" box="[1201,1279,1445,1470]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/3dkp-keqv" name="Museo Civico di Storia Natural de Carmognola" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">MCCI</collectionCode>
